rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0001
rows.name:
Now that I've got Gramps's permission,
just about...I'd better start making
preparations for this mission.

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0002
rows.name:
A hundred grand to spend...that
sure is an exciting prospect!

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0003
rows.name:
I could buy a whole new cutting-edge
salvaging suit...

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0004
rows.name:
But no, I can't splurge this all at once.
The folks back home need this money
more than I do.

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0005
rows.name:
I'll hold off on making any big
purchases, and just head to
Rubirubi's Accessories.

rows.label: fev01_110_125_msg0006
rows.name:
Always best to be prepared for
anything! I might end up fighting
a Crustip like on my last salvage.
